/inventory â€“ View inventory
/sell <item> â€“ Sell an item
/sell_all <rarity> â€“ Sell all items of a rarity
/trade <user> <your_item> <their_item> â€“ Trade items
/fight <user> â€“ Challenge another player

**Admin Commands**
/add_currency <user> <amount> â€“ Add coins
/add_item <rarity> <item> â€“ Add item to rarity
/remove_item <rarity> <item> â€“ Remove item
/add_rarity <name> <chance> â€“ Add rarity
/remove_rarity <name> â€“ Remove rarity
/create_bundle â€“ Create bundle
/edit_bundle â€“ Edit bundle
/delete_bundle â€“ Delete bundle
"""
    await interaction.response.send_message(commands_list, ephemeral=True)

